title: Transneft Western Siberia, JSC continues in-line pipeline inspection (OAO AK Transneft)
text: ( Source : OAO AK Transneft) In September 2015 Specialists of Krasnoyarsk Regional Oil Pipeline Department , Transneft Western Siberia , JSC , carried out in-line inspection of Rybinskaya - Poima section of Omsk - Irkutsk oil trunk pipeline
